12.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers the compensation claims that the insured as a
private individual may incur during his/her journey, through injury to
persons or material damage pursuant to the laws in the country where
the injury or damage is caused.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
12.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Personal injury: DKK 10,000,000
.br
Material damage: DKK 2,000,000
.br
Hotel liability: DKK 25,000
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In this context, 'hotel liability' refers to coverage for damage to a
rented holiday residence/hotel room and the fittings and furnishings of
same.
.br
The sums stated are the maximum amounts that Privatsikring can pay per
year that the insurance is in effect, including interest and costs.
